{"tid":343990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲少女往補習　商場梯間跌倒陷半昏迷","createTime":"2017-08-02T02:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T10:01:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90dda3f5d1ae34a74991f7eaa50dd57a55a26273","tid":343990,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:38:52.000Z","msg":"九龍城一名少女在商場梯間跌倒，頭部撞傷半昏迷送院。今晨9時許，一名17歲少女，穿着校服到九龍城廣場補習，期間在後樓梯跌倒，頭及頸部撞傷，她致電通知父親，其父趕抵商場，見女兒神志不清，隨即報警。少女半昏迷由救護車送院。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉少女傷及頸椎，恐有機會影響神經。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/103851_2733916a8b6973da22ef53c235d79d6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F103851_2733916a8b6973da22ef53c235d79d6c.jpg&h=fe0481a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a662481b3c0eed031d32b916adc7a0bea7fa7331","tid":343990,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e923ac639b2fc99d70f40613bb0b0b9e5beaae7","tid":343990,"uid":48796,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"原來仆街可以咁大鑊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884a183e90285d741ad11ff1505f3cd798287dab","tid":343990,"uid":90166,"like":11,"dislike":56,"score":-45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:59:21.000Z","msg":"點解會去後樓梯？"},{"pid":"03c82333abbb6415a6d635783e4419d3acf1c000","tid":343990,"uid":27777,"like":26,"dislike":8,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會去後樓梯？</blockquote><br />\n關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"889edecbd59fe140f93c20c47ab9e6aa29506375","tid":343990,"uid":85163,"like":20,"dislike":225,"score":-205,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe18915af1a9f092057c7ee561989205b15ad8c","tid":343990,"uid":1790,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03: