quote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會去後樓梯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勞資糾紛</blockquote><br />\n咁撚樣都關事？<br />\n屌你老母啦</blockquote><br />\n連登神探真係無得頂<br />\n以後所有有女人出現既新聞都係勞資糾紛</blockquote><br />\nblock撚左條on9<br />\n又開post伏女<br />\n又咩勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"93584fce84679fda24bd8c8502ee4d323920e836","tid":343990,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"之前睇新聞講過<br />\n有個去台灣讀書既男仔比車撞到<br />\n後腦落地,一個禮拜就死左 係輕輕撞到"},{"pid":"88b1e76ceeb1788df92964b02e65ce614358b151","tid":343990,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前睇新聞講過<br />\n有個去台灣讀書既男仔比車撞到<br />\n後腦落地,一個禮拜就死左 係輕輕撞到</blockquote><br />\n嘉樂仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce8570e01c6d570ee3a1e0d6d29c10fd4756b70","tid":343990,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2a025c223326f128c0013a42e7e8fd6d464f65d","tid":343990,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似大陸咁告個商場賠返一千幾百萬咁樣?"},{"pid":"00f90e64600b23820dcbaf513b4fa6289d236e1b","tid":343990,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"小心"},{"pid":"b5d31449bccc8bc69f3883c47b203360550fb4a0","tid":343990,"uid":61421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會去後樓梯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勞資糾紛</blockquote><br />\n咁撚樣都關事？<br />\n屌你老母啦</blockquote><br />\n連登神探真係無得頂<br />\n以後所有有女人出現既新聞都係勞資糾紛</blockquote><br />\nblock撚左條on9<br />\n又開post伏女<br />\n又咩勞資糾紛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可憐蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab2fa01e06f70bd219bee73debc6eaec7230bf2","tid":343990,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解會去後樓梯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勞資糾紛</blockquote><br />\n你老母日日受服務連登仔啦。"},{"pid":"fd05977e7ece17d589f59d7ed23c883c78151436","tid":343990,"uid":38030,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打比老豆但唔自己報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d野可大可小 點解唔即刻報左警先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想像下嗰一刻都暈都仆街邊諗到咁多，打俾自己最信得過嘅人都合理"},{"pid":"3eb6fd1df0b7b16116bf86fb06dfa7ed1ca2fda5","tid":343990,"uid":22218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九龍城廣場好少會行後樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九龍城廣場要搵後樓梯行真係難過搭電梯"},{"pid":"e3b8b87432836509d142a7d4d2edb756e671f87e","tid":343990,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a87770507974584ed8f7c8f30b94fcd77a8e81","tid":343990,"uid":75694,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:34:58.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - RedBaron )<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad37b63e7e5aa4c7c388de99eee11642069e46d0","tid":343990,"uid":15739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"希望佢無事啦"},{"pid":"00c44033b2dd8ef899a4b362c30238f10e13f823","tid":343990,"uid":96423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起之前仆左幾級樓梯<br />\n腳掌&gt;180度向後屈<br />\n痛到跪左係度郁唔到<br />\n之後諗住死頂行多一層落課室抖抖<br />\n點知我醒返果陣係訓左係地下俾人圍住左<br />\n原來未落多層樓梯我已經暈左<br />\n醒返